				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				HOW TO MASTER POTTERY FOR LESS THAN 20PP<BR>
<BR>
Mastery pottery is easy. Make small bowls until you are blue in the face. Do not fire them. Destroy any successes because you won't reclaim the money you spent to make it. Around the time that you get to a skill of 85 move on to medium bowls. I spent 17PP (Char 95) to get to skill lvl 103. <BR>
<BR>
Naladan Stormcalmer<BR>
Paladin of the 21st Century<BR>
Xev Server
